title: All 32 - Green Bay Packers: Dissecting the Jordan Love pick and Aaron Rodgers future with Aaron Nagler (Football 6/11)
description:
The Packers have had a polarizing offseason and Aaron Nagler of Cheesehead TV is here to break it all down with Will Brinson on the latest edition of 'All 32'. Will and Aaron discuss the controversial selection of Jordan Love (1:00), the thought process behind the pick and next steps for Aaron Rodgers. The guys also analyze Green Bay's defense (14:15) plus set the bar for 2020 after tallying 13 wins last year (17:00).
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
